The Advertising Account Executive is a key member of the Demand team at LiveIntent, driving the company into new accounts, developing strong relationships with Agencies, engaging with new brands and growing LiveIntent&rsquo;s revenue.<br />
LiveIntent is looking for an all-star Account Executive with experience in the Digital Advertising space who is ready to bring a new opportunity to Agency teams. Cultivating relationships with buy-side advertising executives and growing LiveIntent&rsquo;s visibility in the Agency and brand community is a must.</p>
<p>
Having a self-starter attitude and introducing your network to the amazing capabilities of LiveIntent&rsquo;s platform will lead to success at LiveIntent.<br />
The Account Executive will work closely with the National Director of Sales and Chief Revenue Officer of LiveIntent. This is a high visibility position that is powering LiveIntent&rsquo;s growth and domination of the email digital advertising space.<br />
This position requires an understanding of LiveIntent&rsquo;s goals, the ability to learn a new product quickly, a positive attitude, and ability to work in a team environment.<br />
Responsibilities<br />
o Close new business and obtain renewals from client sin the digital advertising space<br />
o Secure budgets and RFPs, build media plans<br />
o Develop a strategic approach to growing business at existing accounts and brining new accounts onto the LiveIntent platform<br />
o Listen to client/needs and goals and develop plans that will be successful upon launch.<br />
o Utilize your existing network while continuing to grow your network among Agencies, Advertisers and brands<br />
o Attend industry events and plan social events with clients</p>
